 Oath and the Question of Fact.\" Translated by Mirhady, David C.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Acropolis_of_Athens_01361.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stub icon\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Acropolis_of_Athens_01361.JPG/40px-Acropolis_of_Athens_01361.JPG\" width=\"40\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Acropolis_of_Athens_01361.JPG/60px-Acropolis_of_Athens_01361.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/37/Acropolis_of_Athens_01361.JPG/80px-Acropolis_of_Athens_01361.JPG 2x\" data-file-width=\"1740\" data-file-height=\"1062\" /></a></td><td><i>This <a href=\"/wiki/Ancient_Greece\" title=\"Ancient Greece\">Ancient Greece</a>&#160;related article is a <a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Stub\" title=\"Wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help Wikipedia by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Heliastic_oath&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a>.</i><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\" style=\"position: absolute; right: 15px; display: none;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:AncientGreece-stub\" title=\"Template:AncientGreece-stub\"><abbr title=\"View this template\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:AncientGreece-stub\" title=\"Template talk:AncientGreece-stub\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\">t</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:AncientGreece-stub&amp;action=edit\"><abbr title=\"Edit this template\">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2233\nCached time: 20180922075341\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.216 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.252 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node 